column5: Was planning on heading to Muskoka this weekend to try my hand on 'thin ice' for some Lake Rosseau brutes ... but the latest forecast for Saturday (at least down here) is 17 !!!! ... I'm already polishing up the golf clubs !
Just so you know, around here, golf is a four letter word
Not if you carry an ultralight in your bag (and give up the 3 iron
Did i put the boat away to early LOL
